snippet.title: WAS JOAN RIVERS MURDERED - WHAT SHE SAID ABOUT MICHELLE OBAMA

localized.description: This video is ONLY speculation. There is absolutely no proof set forth in this video. This administration has called everything into question. Because of what they are doing around the globe and too America, all the lies and deception, it causes caring people to start over turning every rock to find the real truth. I do not wish to offend anyone, I only ask this question. Is this possible and if it is true, what would it mean.
